00:00:35.290 --> 00:00:36.790
is moving those forward.

00:00:36.790 --> 00:00:41.429
As Max said, I've worn a few
different hats at GiveDirectly.

00:00:41.429 --> 00:00:42.970
When I first started
at GiveDirectly,

00:00:42.970 --> 00:00:45.190
I was in Kenya on
the operations side,

00:00:45.190 --> 00:00:48.580
managing our team, signing
