00:18:16.007 --> 00:18:17.590
I mean, for example,
the Malawi thing,

00:18:17.590 --> 00:18:20.030
I just learned about
that yesterday about HIV.

00:18:20.030 --> 00:18:23.320
So you keep learning new things
about cash transfers, which

00:18:23.320 --> 00:18:24.250
