00:19:46.299 --> 00:19:47.836
AUDIENCE: Yeah, I'll go.

00:19:47.836 --> 00:19:49.580
Hey.

00:19:49.580 --> 00:19:54.950
My question is about whether
an organization like yours

00:19:54.950 --> 00:19:59.480
pays a different amount than a
