00:38:11.610 --> 00:38:12.850
through donated dollars.

00:38:12.850 --> 00:38:16.560
And so as concepts, I
think they're complementary

00:38:16.560 --> 00:38:17.470
and both important.

00:38:17.470 --> 00:38:19.142
