00:38:57.270 --> 00:38:59.290
your overall portfolio?

00:38:59.290 --> 00:39:01.730
JOE HUSTON: Yeah.

00:39:01.730 --> 00:39:05.600
And so in general, our
mission is not to--

00:39:05.600 --> 00:39:08.960
we don't have an expand mission.

00:39:08.960 --> 00:39:12.200
We don't have the goal of
be in every country on Earth

00:39:12.200 --> 00:39:16.160
or provide every structure
of cash transfer.

00:39:16.160 --> 00:39:17.850
We're pretty
focused-- well, I'll

00:39:17.850 --> 00:39:19.770
talk about this Houston
and Puerto Rico thing.

00:39:19.770 --> 00:39:22.103
But in general, we're pretty
