00:43:03.110 --> 00:43:05.330
on these feature phones,
the same ones that have

00:43:05.330 --> 00:43:06.740
Snake and things like that.

00:43:06.740 --> 00:43:08.300
You can have a savings account.

00:43:08.300 --> 00:43:10.910
You can draw a loan through
your M-Pesa account.

00:43:10.910 --> 00:43:14.090
Recently, they added the ability
