00:43:31.511 --> 00:43:34.010
a sort of potential for better
outreach and things like that

00:43:34.010 --> 00:43:35.670
from financial institutions.

00:43:35.670 --> 00:43:39.770
There are also small banks
and micro-finance companies

00:43:39.770 --> 00:43:41.900
in Kenya that I could see
potentially moving in.

00:43:41.900 --> 00:43:44.390
I haven't seen that
