Labor is a lot more expensive
to sign people up for cash

00:45:33.340 --> 00:45:35.100
here than in East Africa.

00:45:35.100 --> 00:45:39.980
But there is zero effects for
us and payments are cheaper.

00:45:39.980 --> 00:45:41.740
We're at the debit
cards are basically

00:45:41.740 --> 00:45:43.650
zero fees for us and
for the recipients.

00:45:43.650 --> 00:45:47.620
And so efficiency at the scale
we'll be able to operate at

00:45:47.620 --> 00:45:49.697
is a little bit higher
than our typical program.

